{"tid":2013541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[城邦論plan b?] 民建聯兩會建議大灣區起「香港城」 當地建立港式學校 港式金融等予港人","createTime":"2020-05-12T11:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T11:04:32.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf054f5a27948c8cfabba4feebf92f2e686aa97","tid":2013541,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:01:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200512/s00002/1589222712368/%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%83%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%B5%B7%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200512%2Fs00002%2F1589222712368%2F%25E3%2580%2590emily%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259F%258E%25E3%2580%258D&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=ec65ae65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200512%2Fs00002%2F1589222712368%2F%25E3%2580%2590emily%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259F%258E%25E3%2580%258D&h=820b6e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200512/s00002/1589222712368/%E3%80%90emily%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%83%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%B5%B7%E3%80%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】「兩會」本月底北京舉行，民建聯人大代表、政協委員噚日公布多項建議，包括喺大灣區兩個選址建造「香港城」等。萬一兩會期間《國歌法》恢復二讀，撞期點算好？港區人大代表葉國謙話，民建聯會以重要立法工作為先；政協兼立法會議員梁志祥就話未知邊個會期討論，但極力爭取以政協委員身分參加會議。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯噚日公布23項建議，涵蓋金融、土地、教育等多項議題。主席李慧琼提議喺珠海市桂山島，以及港珠澳大橋珠海段南側指定水域填海建造香港城，每處可以提供最少10平方公里嘅未發展用地，可提供大量住屋單位，亦可打造成新型經濟中心。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼亦建議加強推廣中國傳統文化，完善香港學校同內地交流學習嘅機制等。<br />\n<br />\n港區人代陳勇就話，水資源關鍵，認為東江水負擔好重，建議將「統包」總額由每年8.2億立方米減至7億立方米、超出上限用水則以「按量付費」模式畀錢。此外，新冠肺炎令野味問題備受關注，梁志祥認為要研究立法全面禁食貓狗，並用國家宣傳教育機器，強調食用貓狗嘅安全風險，又建議設立群眾舉報平台。"},{"pid":"a1a2752c64871bd370549f38a6295b1a90fe443c","tid":2013541,"uid":88878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:03:05.000Z","msg":"死都唔比人做中國人<br />\n返左中國住都要買東江水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016837dd9b8eb75febb714c7395e97b45783cd9b","tid":2013541,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"如果我係呢班垃圾嘅背後老細，比晒錢竟然得呢啲表面，我一定剷撚死佢地再炒撚晒佢地"},{"pid":"9648370219e3b134d4f02c82a1faa721f1092e02","tid":2013541,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"016837dd9b8eb75febb714c7395e97b45783cd9b","tid":2013541,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"如果我係呢班垃圾嘅背後老細，比晒錢竟然得呢啲表面，我一定剷撚死佢地再炒撚晒佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"*表現"}]}